            <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-xl mb-2">Should YouTubers build a website or focus only on YouTube?</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Build both. Website = algorithm insurance. YouTube = discovery. TechReviewDaily lost 67% AdSense revenue overnight from algorithm change. Creators with email lists lost 23% average. Why? Email list = YOUR platform, YouTube's = rental. Strategy: Use YouTube for audience building, website for monetization. Email capture on every video description. Sponsor media kit on your site (3.2x higher CPM). Membership platform you control (YouTube takes 30% cut, your site takes 0%). Merch store with better margins (68% vs. 35% Amazon). YouTube gets viewers to your site. Your site converts them into revenue YOU control.</p>
